<p>The good news is that help is still available! Telemedicine visits are here. You can now make an appointment and get in touch with a doctor to renew your medication or discuss medical issue.  </p>
    
<p>The best way to do this is to register with us using the button below. Just enter your health card number, email and set a password. If you visited our clinic before, you will have immediate access to your patient record and will be able to book your first visit. This site is secured by SSL certificate, just like your bank's website. Visits booked here have priority over direct phone calls, so we encourage everybody to register and save time for you and a doctor. Spelling names and numbers over the phone is time consuming and error-prone. 
</p>

